snippet.title: SteamWorld Tower Defense - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
SteamWorld Tower Defense is an action-packed strategy game, available for download in the Nintendo DSi Shop. This trailer shows a few clips from the various levels of the game.

For more information about SteamWorld Tower Defense, visit http://www.steamworldtd.com.
